name: Rocket Launch (JamzDEV)
description:
Rocket Launch is a new game I have created. It is a casual arcade game where you fly through a dense asteroid field, collecting power rods to buy new ships while trying to get the highest score possible!

The game is designed to be a mobile game, but has a web build so the game can be enjoyed on desktop computers.

The game will release on Google Play in a few days; a link will be added to this page when it does. I would greatly appreciate it if you gave it a go there as it really supports me!
